m Lesolang\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"a\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://theuncommonpractice.substack.com\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] text-[#B8654A] hover:text-[#B8654A]/80 hover:underline font-sans font-medium\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"(Subscribe on Substack)\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xs text-card-foreground/60 font-sans\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Hypnotherapist \\u0026 Peak Performance Coach\\\"}]]}]]}]]}],\\\"$undefined\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"prose-custom\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"You are walking around silently expecting people to show up for you when they've watched you break your own promises to yourself.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"2\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Think about that for a second.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"You told yourself you'd start that project in January. It's June. You told yourself you'd go to the gym this week. It's Thursday and you haven't packed your bag. You told yourself you'd stop accepting the treatment you don't deserve. You accepted it again yesterday.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"6\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"And then you wonder why your partner doesn't take your needs seriously. Why your boss doesn't respect your boundaries. Why your friends don't call as often as they used to.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"8\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"They are mirroring your relationship with yourself back to you.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",\\\"10\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-foreground font-serif mt-12 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Invisible Curriculum\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"12\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Every promise you break to yourself is a lesson you teach everyone around you. Not through words — through demonstration. You are broadcasting, 24 hours a day, what treatment is acceptable. And the people in your life are learning from it.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"14\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"When you say you'll wake up at 5am and you hit snooze until 7, you are not just failing a morning routine. You are training everyone who depends on you that your word is negotiable. When you say you'll stop drinking, stop scrolling, stop settling — and you don't — you are not just disappointing yourself. You are lowering the bar for how seriously anyone has to take you.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"16\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"The cruelest part? Most of the people around you aren't even conscious of it. They can't articulate why they don't trust your follow-through. They just feel it. They feel the gap between what you say and what you do. And they adjust their expectations accordingly.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",\\\"18\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-foreground font-serif mt-12 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Relationship Mirror\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"20\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Here is what I see in my practice, over and over: people come in wanting their partner to show up differently. More present. More reliable. More emotionally available. And I ask them one question: \\\\\\\"When was the last time you showed up for yourself like that?\\\\\\\"\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"22\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"The silence is always the same length.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"24\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"You cannot give what you do not have. You cannot demand what you do not demonstrate. If you are unreliable with yourself, you will attract people who are unreliable with you. If you tolerate your own excuses, you will tolerate theirs. If you abandon yourself when things get hard, you will find partners who do the same.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"26\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"This is not punishment. This is alignment. The universe is not punishing you — it is matching you.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",\\\"28\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-foreground font-serif mt-12 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Repair\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"30\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"The fix is not complicated. It is just uncomfortable.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"32\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Start with one promise. A small one. Something you can keep today. Not next week. Not on Monday. Today.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"34\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Drink the water. Make the call. Write the sentence. Send the email. Show up at the time you said you would. Not for anyone else. For you.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"36\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"And when you keep it — and you will — notice what happens. Not in your schedule. In your nervous system. Something shifts. A thread of trust, thin as spider silk, reconnects between your word and your action.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"38\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Keep that thread. Build on it. Tomorrow, make another promise. Keep that one too.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"40\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Over time, the people around you will notice. Not because you told them. Because the broadcast changes. The signal shifts. You start walking differently. Speaking differently. Occupying space differently. And the people who were mirroring your self-abandonment will either rise to meet you or fall away.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"42\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Both outcomes are progress.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",\\\"44\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-foreground font-serif mt-12 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Bottom Line\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"46\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"You cannot expect others to show up for you in ways you have not shown up for yourself. It is not fair to them. It is not kind to you.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"48\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"The relationship you want starts with the one you are willing to have with yourself. Not tomorrow. Not when you're ready. Now.\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"50\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-card-foreground/90 font-sans leading-[1.85] mb-6 text-base\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"Show up. Keep showing up. Watch what happens.\\\"}}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L16\\\",null,{\\\"title\\\":\\\"You Can't Expect Others to Show Up When You Don't Show Up for Yourself\\\",\\\"slug\\\":\\\"you-cant-expect-others-to-show-up-when-you-dont-show-up-for-yourself\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-16 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-8 text-center shadow-sm\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-bold text-foreground font-serif\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Ready to talk about what you just read?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-2 text-sm text-card-foreground/80 font-sans max-w-md mx-auto\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Book a free discovery call with Hakeem Lesolang. No pressure. No pitch. Just an honest conversation about where you are and where you want to be.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"a\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://calendly.com/folasessions/discovery-call\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#121212] text-[#F5F2EC] px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold font-sans hover:bg-[#232323] transition-all hover:shadow-md\\\",\\\"children